data.description: Beautiful Meritage Home built in 2021!**Seller will contribute to buyers closing costs with an acceptable offer**. Convenient Location for Lackland AFB.  Freshly painted interior! Carpet only in the bedrooms! Spacious Open Floor Plan with Beautiful Kitchen, Breakfast Bar, Granite Counter Tops, Gas Cooking, and Large Dining Room which can be a very flexible space; owners used this as a playroom or could be an office space. Covered Patio with Wood Accent Feature for Added Privacy Outdoor TV to remain. Neighborhood has a Pool and Playground for your enjoyment. Seller had Gutters added to the exterior of the home. $4K Water Softener to remain. This is also wired as a smart home.  Builder Warranty conveys to new owner.
